133
00:09:58,739 --> 00:10:00,020
This is a hard time.

134
00:10:00,020 --> 00:10:05,020
for David and he's in distress and it leads him to God.

135
00:10:05,620 --> 00:10:09,020
By the way, the problems that we face in life,

136
00:10:09,020 --> 00:10:12,740
