195
00:13:16,900 --> 00:13:18,180
That's amazing.

196
00:13:18,180 --> 00:13:21,100
No one else, everyone else was just sitting in the boat.

197
00:13:21,940 --> 00:13:24,340
Peter says, Lord, if it be thou, bid me come to thee.

198
00:13:25,340 --> 00:13:26,940
And you know, Peter got out of that boat

