00:15:13,460 --> 00:15:14,900
I'm looking to Jesus.

235
00:15:15,340 --> 00:15:17,940
I'm looking towards the Lord

236
00:15:17,940 --> 00:15:21,940
because he's the one that can give me what I need.

237
00:15:21,940 --> 00:15:24,620
We could apply this verse in verse number 15

238
00:15:24,620 --> 00:15:27,900
