240
00:15:29,060 --> 00:15:31,380
His eyes are on the Lord and it's only the Lord

241
00:15:31,380 --> 00:15:33,380
that can give him the peace that he needs

242
00:15:33,380 --> 00:15:35,140
in the time of distress.

243
00:15:35,140 --> 00:15:37,460
His eyes are on the Lord and it's only the Lord

244
00:15:37,460 --> 00:15:40,060
that can give him the direction that he needs

245
00:15:40,060 --> 00:15:42,860
in a time of chaos and uncertainty.

246
00:15:42,860 --> 00:15:45,260
His eyes are on the Lord and it's only the Lord

247
00:15:45,260 --> 00:15:48,060
that can give him the forgiveness that he needs.

248
00:15:49,620 --> 00:15:52,540
This evening, I don't know what it is that you need.

249
00:15:52,540 --> 00:15:55,780
I know that those three things are specifically,

250
00:15:55,780 --> 00:15:59,620
clearly revealed to us through the text of Scripture

251
00:15:59,620 --> 00:16:02,620
in these few verses of Psalm 25.

252
00:16:02,620 --> 00:16:05,700
And I don't know what your need might be tonight,

253
00:16:05,700 --> 00:16:08,540
but can I tell you that God can meet your need?

254
00:16:09,020 --> 00:16:10,820
We got to get our eyes on the Lord.

255
00:16:11,740 --> 00:16:13,180
Listen, I understand we're living

256
00:16:13,180 --> 00:16:15,540
in some really interesting times, aren't we?

257
00:16:16,860 --> 00:16:20,380
I mean, look, we're living in some very interesting times.

